
hosted at:

    http://blazingcloud.heroku.com

to run it locally:

    bundle
    foreman start

# we added an endpoint to post to for each deploy
10092  heroku addons:add deployhooks:http  url=http://blazingcloud.net/incoming/deploy/heroku --remote heroku
# Incoming deploy hooks from other sites require 
# these envs to send a message -- testing --WIP

10093  heroku config:add DEPLOY_TWILIO_ACCOUNTSID=__ACCOUNT_SID
10095  heroku config:add DEPLOY_TWILIO_AUTHTOKEN=___TOKEN



note: http://blog.blazingcloud.net is hosted at Media Temple and is implemented in WordPress
